            <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-100">
              Cooking and enjoying food and drinks are my hobbies outside of web
              development. With No ReservAItions, I've found a way to mix the
              two. I'm using ChatGPT to create reviews for the places that I
              visit in the spirit of Anthony Bourdain and I'm having so much fun
              with it!
            </p>
